"{\n  \"correct\": \"no\",\n  \"explanation\": \"The code is using sns.FacetGrid.map() with sns.lmplot(), which is incorrect. sns.lmplot() is a figure-level function and should not be used with sns.FacetGrid.map(). The map() function in FacetGrid is used to apply a plotting function to each facet of the grid. Instead, sns.regplot() should be used with sns.FacetGrid.map().\",\n  \"patch\": \"6c6\\n< g.map(sns.lmplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n---\\n> g.map(sns.regplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n\"\n}"